Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:16.08,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,I was born into this world to seek her,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:23.97,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,sacrificing all of the things I would have\Ngained from a new life somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:37.24,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,The girl made my body from scrap she had collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.21,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,My memory is stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.53,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,I cannot recall anything even if I exert effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:54.74,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Where I had been until now, or where I was trying to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:07.79,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:11.81,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,I cannot talk with the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:19.73,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,But this is the one and only warmth I seek in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:26.51,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Although, since I am made of scrap, I cannot feel that very warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:02.90,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,414)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:02.90,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}Once More After Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm not a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:12.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You always confuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.99,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Next time, crawl in on all fours\Nso I know you're not a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How's Furukawa doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.23,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming, but she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just so you know, she wasn't calling\Nyour name in her sleep or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:26.87,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't be so full of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never asked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If she were to say anything, it'd be this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,“Oh, Dad, I love you!”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.75,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,“You're so cool.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,“You match so well with my beautiful mother!”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't make me look like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You did it on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.62,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.10,San,San,0,0,0,,Are you here to visit Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard she's stuck in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.27,San,San,0,0,0,,No, she only has a mild fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:52.43,San,San,0,0,0,,It's just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.30,San,San,0,0,0,,…Nagisa is physically weak to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.40,San,San,0,0,0,,She was away from school for a\Nlong period of time last year, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:05.64,San,San,0,0,0,,so the doctor said to keep her in bed today to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:11.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Anyways, thanks to you carrying her back,\Nit didn't turn out as badly as it could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.04,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's Sanae's bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A token of our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I didn't come here for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.32,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,There were obviously going to be\Nsome leftovers anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.43,San,San,0,0,0,,So my… my bread is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.64,San,San,0,0,0,,…is Furukawa Bread's dead weight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:46.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess there really isn't much to worry about after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.10,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.60,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Where is the staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They just ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take it if you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.81,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. They gave it to me for free anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.61,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.32,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Say thank you to Sanae-san and her husband for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's so stupid. She knew she's physically weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:21.77,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:22.80,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:24.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.78,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Look at this dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.05,Default,Man,0,0,0,,A construction tool fell and did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.35,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Will you be my witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.79,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's despicable of you to drag an unrelated person into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:41.19,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Without a witness, you'd run away, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.07,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Like I've said multiple times, I didn't drop any tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.00,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,And if I had, I wouldn't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.73,Default,Man,0,0,0,,How can I trust that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.10,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If you're telling me to pay the repair fee, then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.43,Default,Man,0,0,0,,So you admit you did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.78,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,No, I just want you to reflect\Non this one day and wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.96,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,…if what the electrician that day said was true or false.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.67,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,At a place where you feel most content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.36,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Next to the person you find most dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.63,Default,Man,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.69,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,People's lives are repetitions of inflicting pain on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.00,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's understandable to doubt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:23.46,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,But being unable to trust anything is the same as being unable to feel other people's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.30,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Aren't you, perhaps, feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.92,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Aren't you, perhaps, living slavishly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.67,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Are you able to laugh with an honest heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.03,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I think so…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:32.89,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.46,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Then you must be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.38,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Please keep living so that love doesn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:44.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm amazed at how he can spout all those sick lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:49.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was probably a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:52.97,Default,2,0,0,0,,Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Look at it from this angle, and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.57,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:03.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm willing to bet a cat jumped off that wall and made the dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.01,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Thank you. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I only said what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.91,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'd like to give proper thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.14,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Give me a call when you have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:33.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like, “aren't you living alone”,\Nor “are you smiling”, and other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.25,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,He's the legendary MC…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,He's {\i1}the{\i0\fscx30.303} {\r} Yoshino Yuusuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:39.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:42.92,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hell yeah. He's a retired charismatic musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,He had CDs out and was pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,He had gone missing, but who knew he was around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I have “The Best of” my little sister made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wait. You have a little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah. I never told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara's little sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet she looks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yoshino Yuusuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:17.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:20.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Sakagami Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.17,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Maybe she's actually a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Girls can't possibly be stronger than guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,He's cross-dressing and deceiving the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you seriously saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I'll prove to you that he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:47.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,At this moment, Sunohara had yet to realize\Nhe had begun to walk the path of the pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can totally hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.86,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:57.07,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I didn't come for a fight today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I just wanted to chat a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Listen to what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I overslept this morning, so I was totally shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.08,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Tehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.48,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Your character's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:13.35,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And when I tried to shave, it turns out that\Nthe razor was chipped, so it really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So if you don't mind, can I borrow your razor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.07,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Why do I have to lend one to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yay! He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You heard it, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I did, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.09,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You just said, “Why do I have to lend one to you?”, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In other words, you own a razor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Which means—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.57,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't own one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:40.04,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,When I said “why”, I meant, “Why should I lend you my personal possessions?”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.20,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,First of all…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,First of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.85,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's rude to ask such a thing of a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:50.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:51.95,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:21.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:25.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I found the courage to wave at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:33.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I thought that you might not forgive me, since I hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Now that I feel relieved…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You might be an idiot, but I don't think there's anything wrong with that. {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You think so? {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since I'm an idiot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm on the same level as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:15.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Far away from those who can handle\Nthe world well or can take risky gambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:21.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet there's a lot of stress to handle,\Nbut if it means crying alone, come get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I mean, since I've got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hanging around with you keeps me free from boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay. I will call you when I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.67,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Searching for the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:49.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:51.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.16,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How's your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.77,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.96,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:57.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:58.20,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It hurts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.48,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It looks like you're in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:03.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Give me five!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.78,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Dribble…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.18,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,From there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.50,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.50,Default,2,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It hurts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.41,Default,Fun,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It really does look like you're in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then we'll do boxer and trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're the trainer, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:24.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You position your hands like this,\Nand I'll punch them repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,O-Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You say, “One! Two! One! Two!”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:30.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:31.62,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:32.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Jab! Jab! Straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.40,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,One! Two! One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.67,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,One! Two! One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.18,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,One! Two! One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:42.81,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,One—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How long are you going to say that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:46.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's the chime. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:48.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:48.96,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.76,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wha? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a star, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:01.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara, you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's after school already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Classes are over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, about a hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've slept for a hundred years after being kicked by Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is a world a hundred years since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! What happened to\Nthe rest of the world then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:29.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:34.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Father. Mother. I'm apologize for being an idiot to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll live to my fullest even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wake up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The hologram kicked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:44.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm actually a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then when you said the world ended…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:48.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.12,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:53.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Father. Mother. I'm sorry I was such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:56.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll live to my fullest with the Okazaki cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't believe you can keep it going for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You were lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You believed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I would, since I was half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey! You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.09,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.80,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi. Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.39,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.12,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I-It's way too cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:19.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's a charm about it you don't find in cats or dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.96,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi. Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:27.86,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi! Puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Oh come on, don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.23,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi! Puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.24,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi! Puhi! Puhi! Puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It doesn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.37,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Compared to Tomoyo's kick, which hurt more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You've got other things to ask, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I think I saw something light blue along with the sole of the shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.02,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Erase it from your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.02,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.25,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing to my baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:09.87,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah, an urinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.21,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A baby boar. You hear people call them uribou, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.06,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did it come to get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:18.10,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Her name's Botan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:19.29,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.04,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's a really pretty name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sounds so delectable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.52,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.77,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Here Botan, say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.50,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A new friend for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.18,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi! Puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Practice for the open house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. My guess is that you don't\Ndeal with that stuff very well, do you? {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:44.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I figured that we could look for reference material on how to do speeches and presentations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Would we find one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.59,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.30,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Is there something I can do for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.02,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Or would you like me to serve you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have a hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,O-Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.62,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll get it ready right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.18,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Please have a seat and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.46,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.30,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.21,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,My name is Miyazawa Yukine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:24.02,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,So you're Okazaki Tomoya-san and Furukawa Nagisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:27.04,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,This is your first time coming here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.20,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,That's how I think of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.41,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I really like this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This place used to be a library, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.73,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It still is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.66,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,All the books that do not get read often are gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.52,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It's like the second library.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.17,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,There are old video tapes and records, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Phew. I thought this place had turned into a cafe behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:58.30,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I get various people visiting from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.30,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:06.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm just thinking that there are lots of unique people at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or, maybe it's this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:16.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Speak as though I'm just a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Calm yourself and speak loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:20.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, I'm Furukawa Nagisa from 3-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:27.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Uh… Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Keep it up! What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:35.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The reason why I decided to bring the drama club back is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:41.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you want to act when you're like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Besides, do you have any experience in acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. I'm a complete amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't know any of the details behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And the president reveals the unfortunate truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What kind of play will we be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What kind of play…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are lots of genres, from musicals to plays for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Realistic modern ones to surreal ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, then you'd better answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You said there was a play you wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:16.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a really, really fun play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's so vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it a comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:27.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean to say that it'll be purely humorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then there are tear-jerking moments, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes and no…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it humorous or tear-jerking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,S-Somewhere in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fine, you pass. Since you were at least trying to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Next question, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:50.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What was the picture on the flier about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's the Big Dango Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Answered without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:56.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The nationally-renowned characters\Nthat any Japanese person would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's the Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous that there's a hundred of them. It sounds like it's always fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:07.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think it'd be big trouble if they all went to an amusement park at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But they're—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:13.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't start talking so eloquently!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The gap in your enthusiasm would drive people away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a bad thing to have a positive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:24.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure about being so much more\Npassionate when explaining the Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:29.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right. That would make this\Nan open house for the Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like we have a lot of walls to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:37.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,First and foremost, why do you want to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have zero experience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Because I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What about it do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I felt it'd be fun to act with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:53.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little, I couldn't act in\Nschool performances since I'd be sick on those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:58.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I would be absent from school often,\Nso I couldn't participate in practice, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's why I have such a fascination with acting alongside friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I had a clear desire to join\Nthe drama club in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:09.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And also to give acting my\Nbest effort for those three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:15.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I couldn't attend school often, even in high school…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I was absent for a long time my senior year, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I still want to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:29.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't know anything, and it might be really bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,but I want to give it my best as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:36.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To work on one thing as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think that's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Things like that, I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…simply love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:56.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think you should say that in the open house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How should I say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think you were able to say\Neverything you had on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really? {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I usually say exactly what I think. {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, you do. {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It hurts sometimes. {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:10.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So believe in your own words. {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes…{ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Furukawa Nagisa. {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes! {ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will people come to the open house?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We'll never know until it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:29.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But we posted so many fliers,\Nso if two or three people show up—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We put a flier up here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:42.09,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,If it's the flier that was up there,\NI saw a student council member taking it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Took it down? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:47.09,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Probably because you didn't get their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.09,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,You two put those up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then all the others placed around the school got…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.18,Default,PA,0,0,0,,Furukawa Nagisa-san from 3-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.98,Default,PA,0,0,0,,Please report to the student council room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.47,Default,PA,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.78,Default,PA,0,0,0,,Furukawa Nagisa-san from 3-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.60,Default,PA,0,0,0,,Please report to the student council room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:04.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa…
