Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:41.80,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:46.54,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So give me advice on what to say\Nin order to get on Tomoyo's good side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:53.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:54.78,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You look great in your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:56.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In other words—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:23:59.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm really different this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:02.34,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,“First of all”?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:07.72,Default,2,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Home run!
